```nix
{ pkgs, ... }:
{
  config.programs.steam = {
    enable = true;
    extraCompatPackages = [
      pkgs.proton-ge-bin
    ];
  };
}
```

## Summary

The file sets up Steam on a NixOS system by:
- Enabling the Steam program through `enable = true`
- Adding "Proton-GE (Glorious Eggroll)" as an extra compatibility package, which allows running Windows games on Linux through compatibility layers

This configuration would typically be included in a NixOS `configuration.nix` or home-manager setup to provide gaming capabilities with enhanced Proton support.

